  VARIABLES
         Is the container to storing something like the data.
         To declare the variables for using the three ways on it
                ( *let = using only between the block only,value  can change. )            
                 ( *const = using for set the value to be constant not to be anywhere)
                 ( *var = declare and used anywhere within or without the block it can be used ,to change the value anywhere.)
ex:
   {var a= 10;                o?p:   10
   }
 console.log(a)
   {
    let a = 10;                o?p:   error (a is not defined)reason :it only acess in bet the block)
}
  console.log(a)
 (const a=10;
a=70;                          o?p :  error because iot not to change declared in the constant
console.log(a)

