    KEYWORDS
       predefined words it have few code all ready written if frequently using thing by anyone 
     COMMENTS
       one thing defining the thing to user but not made any changes in output the code
             single line comment(//...................)
             multiline comment(/*---------------------*/)

     OPERATORS
  arithimitic opertor
       Perform the operations between the operandsusing the operators.
        +  addition
        -  subtraction
        *  multiplication
        /  division
        // floor division
        %  modulo
        ++ increament (++a preincreament,a++postincreament)
        -- decreament (--a predecreament,a-- postdecreament)
        etc.......
   datatype
     to define  what type of data should be stored in the variable.
                      typeof()  
        ex:    console.log(typeof(10))
      types:
           Primitive                                  
           Non primitive
      primitive:
            boolean,string,null,undefined,number
      non-primitive
            object
            array
